org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601

Class ControlCommands

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601.ControlCommands
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, INestedKlvValue, ISpecialFraming, IUasDatalinkValue

    public class ControlCommands
extends Object
implements IUasDatalinkValue, INestedKlvValue, ISpecialFraming
    Control Commands.

    This class represents any number (zero or more) of ControlCommand packs that may occur within an ST 0601 Local Set. Unlike most of the entries supported in ST 0601, ControlCommand can repeat.
